thread.title: Claire Campbell
thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Claire Campbell

author: Claire Campbell
title: Claire Campbell
text: My advisor, Gowan, was extremely helpful. My fiance and I had been struggling to find room blocks for our wedding guests, and then I found Skipper. In no time at all, we had 2 agreements with hotels for more than enough rooms. Gowan was on top of things and always there to help out.
